  "timeline": {
    "application_processing_time_md": {
      "en": "EMGS states a 14-working-day client charter for a complete application, while incomplete or incorrect documents can add time. A Student Pass is usually issued for up to one year at a time and may be renewed subject to the approved study duration and conditions.",
      "zh-Hans": "EMGS 说明，完整申请的客户服务时限为 14 个工作日，但材料不完整或错误可能延长时间。学生准证通常一次签发最长一年，并可根据获批学习期限和条件续签。"
    },
